## rv_na_gallery — the two packs the Pixel Crawler sweeps missed (2026-07-18):
## Raven Fantasy Icons (rv_* — a full 32px item-icon library: potions, food,
## crafting matter, quest curios, gear) and Ninja Adventure's animals (the
## livestock/wildlife gap — villages had no living thing that wasn't trying
## to kill you). Everything here is PLACEHOLDER (dev-launcher Future tab
## only) until a quest / profession / zone promotes it: drop the flag and
## give it a real home. Format: scripts/content/README.md.
class_name RvNaGallery

